{"tid":99380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普繼與英國首相會面後 一日內熱線與日德俄法澳5國元首通話","createTime":"2017-01-29T07:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T10:21:08.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94d60a6a92c6866772fe565145f79a337b5085dd","tid":99380,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"川普一日之內熱線5國元首 與安倍敲定2月10日高峰會 <br />\n<img src=\"http://upmediawebmag.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20170129125105911340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupmediawebmag.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20170129125105911340.jpg&h=c0233c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 川普20日上任後馬不停蹄地推動政策之餘，也密切與他國元首熱線互動。28日，川普一口 氣安排與日本首相安倍晉三、德國總理梅克爾（Angela Merkel）、俄國總統普京（Vladi mir Putin）、法國總統奧朗德（Francois Hollande）、澳洲總理騰博爾（Malcolm Turn bull）等5國元首通話。 繼川普27日與英國首相梅伊（Theresa May）會面後，白宮發言人史派瑟（Sean Spicer） 27日即在其官方推特上（twitter）預告川普隔日的通話行程。梅伊為川普20日上任後首 位面對面會談的國家元首。<br />\n<a href=\"http://upmediawebmag.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=11443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupmediawebmag.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D11443&d=tV9qdyV9zZdslbmYcqdCeEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b2ec5cda\" target=\"_blank\">http://upmediawebmag.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=11443</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時到中國？"},{"pid":"e00315f9a560737252efd440624a12422d3ca609","tid":99380,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"打黎香港會點"},{"pid":"5899498cb99bb8a91d120dcb5e49efdecea8ef8e","tid":99380,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打黎香港會點</blockquote><br />\nkung hei fat choi"},{"pid":"f5a71d3eeedabe4baf5fcd9c1b230ee63c219a32","tid":99380,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3137236248a7a595528c07de88b25bb19612f94e","tid":99380,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201